<!--模拟整合-->
<view class="wz-box">
  <view class="wz-contain">
  <view class="wz-item">区域介绍</view>
  <view class="wz-item">区域剪影</view>
  <view class="wz-item">行程预约</view>
  <view class="wz-item">在线客服</view>
  </view>
</view>



<view class="introduce">
  <view class="js-content">
    <text class="paragraph">  黄花镇村是北京市怀柔区九渡河镇下辖村，相邻黄花村、四渡河村、撞道口村，空气好，交通便利，依山傍水。</text>
    <text class="paragraph">  2019年9月24日，黄花镇村（黄花镇蓝莓）入选第九批全国“一村一品”示范村镇名单。</text>
    <text class="paragraph">  主要农产品：桃子、杨桃、大芋头。</text>
    <text class="paragraph">  村内资源：钛铁矿、磁赤铁矿、粘土、铅、氟镁石。</text>
    <text class="paragraph">  企事业单位：北京奥博德装饰工程有限公司，李联合运输站，北京供电公司怀柔供电分公司黄花城供电所，北京鑫华光模具厂，北京安通电力设备安装有限公司。</text>
  </view>
</view>


<view class="jy-container">
  <view class="jianying-image">
    <image class="image-placeholder" src="" mode="aspectFit"></image>
  </view>
  <view class="jianying-image">
    <image class="image-placeholder" src="" mode="aspectFit"></image>
  </view>
</view>


<view class="reserve">
  <picker mode="date" class="picker">
    <view class="picker-placeholder">日期</view>
  </picker>
  <picker mode="selector" class="picker" range="{{[1, 2, 3, 4, 5]}}">
    <view class="picker-placeholder">人数</view>
  </picker>

  <view class="options">
  <checkbox-group class="checkbox-group">
    <view class="checkbox-row">
      <label class="checkbox-item"><checkbox value="1" /> 选项1</label>
      <label class="checkbox-item"><checkbox value="2" /> 选项2</label>
    </view>
    <view class="checkbox-row">
      <label class="checkbox-item"><checkbox value="3" /> 选项3</label>
      <label class="checkbox-item"><checkbox value="4" /> 选项4</label>
    </view>
  </checkbox-group>
</view>

<view class="button-contain">
  <button size="mini" plain bindtap="makeReservation">确定</button>
</view>
</view>



<view class="chat-container">
  <view class="message-box">
    <view class="customer">客服</view>
    <view class="self">我</view>
  </view>
  <view class="input-container">
  <textarea class="text-input" placeholder="请输入"></textarea>
  <button bindtap="sendMessage">发送</button>
  </view>
</view>
